vnoremap <S-Tab> <gv

" Save with enter
function! keyboard#should_save_on_enter()
  return bufname('%') !=# 'swoopBuf' && empty(&buftype)
endfunction
nnoremap <silent> <expr> <CR> keyboard#should_save_on_enter() ? ':call SaveIfUnsaved()<CR>' : '<CR>'

